<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I cancelled my accounts.
<br />

<br />
The game and my class was no longer fun.  I tried not playing last weekend and discovered real life is much more fun and rewarding.  I'm a lot happier now.
<br />

<br />
I would like to actually thank Sony.  Making the game such a boring, grind where skills don't count and nerfing my class's core abilities is what made the game annoying and unenjoyable.  Thank you for making it easier to leave.  Life is so much better than EQ.
<br />

<br />
Good luck to all who remain behind.  May you find enjoyment.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
